{"body": "Hey @kennyj, I'm a little bit worried this may make the test more brittle. Lets say tomorrow mysql changes the error message, we'll never know because the test will continue passing - I know it's unlikely to happen, but who knows.\r\n\r\nAlso, I think that testing the message below already gives you certainty that any syntax error happened, and that the database name was properly quoted in the executed sql.\r\n\r\n    `Unknown database 'foo-bar': SHOW TABLES IN `foo-bar`\r\n\r\nWhat do you think?\r\n@rafaelfranca thoughs?", "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/comments/4351709", "created_at": "2012-03-06T19:55:43Z", "html_url": "https://github.com/rails/rails/pull/5306#issuecomment-4351709", "updated_at": "2012-03-06T19:55:43Z", "repo": "rails", "issue_id": 5306, "user": {"following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/carlosantoniodasilva/following{/other_user}", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/carlosantoniodasilva/events{/privacy}", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/carlosantoniodasilva/orgs", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/carlosantoniodasilva", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/carlosantoniodasilva/gists{/gist_id}", "html_url": "https://github.com/carlosantoniodasilva", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/carlosantoniodasilva/subscriptions", "avatar_url": "https://1.gravatar.com/avatar/77237b97a465ae5a293ad323b7296837?d=https%3A%2F%2Fidenticons.github.com%2F60b997fd68261ce70cadaf6c8226c042.png", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/carlosantoniodasilva/repos", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/carlosantoniodasilva/received_events", "gravatar_id": "77237b97a465ae5a293ad323b7296837", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/carlosantoniodasilva/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "login": "carlosantoniodasilva", "type": "User", "id": 26328, "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/carlosantoniodasilva/followers"}, "owner": "rails", "_id": {"$oid": "523819